name: shining rust
description:
"shining rust" by byng

honestly, I didn't expect much from this image when I took it, with the sun shining directly on the wheel. The direct reflection of the sun made the rusty iron look stunning, but hey! this is film format, sometimes we are disappointed with the results that do not match our expectations. but damn, this one looks so beautiful

the gear I use;
* Camera : Fujica MPF 105XN (35mm camera)
* Lens : EBC X-Fujinon f=1.6 50mm DM
* Film : Cira Film 200

overexposure +1 with normal develop on local lab
